{"about_the_game":"Skala is a game about changing the physical scale of things. You can make yourself large enough to step over a giant cliff, or make a key small enough to be passed through a solid wall. The game explores the consequences of this rescaling mechanic through simple yet difficult puzzles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884990/extras/skala-gif.gif?t=1720814990\" /><br><i>A level where you have to stretch yourself in order to reach a star.</i><br><br>Skala takes place in a graphically simple world with a big house and a star filled sky to explore. The world is covered by a relaxing soundtrack which let's you take in all of the games mechanics.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884990/extras/living-room.png?t=1720814990\" /><br><br>There are over 70 puzzle levels to play through. Every level is unique and has some purpose, whether it's  introducing a new idea/mechanic, or developing on the concepts of previous levels.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Green","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1884990/c3950c5571b19ef03d911ec777bcaaa398735c50.jpg"},{"name":"Unlocked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1884990/8e3eb55732fd6ed47279200d85e60a4bde19392c.jpg"},{"name":"Opposite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1884990/5fefea57a144e33b2049c88f587a4afc271bb7fe.jpg"},{"name":"Observer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1884990/a96ff1834215111fbfd2a39033e4512bc54795a9.jpg"},{"name":"Flow","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1884990/3a2c30131b3458052de6933a8210001a79c35857.jpg"},{"name":"Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1884990/5c33d2777cc4672a5bc5403503074de34